{"tid":20619,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Moto 未打算推出 Moto360 新作 ","createTime":"2016-12-03T12:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T05:30:18.000Z","uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d38680396d70659a7dd23bfe0fc8e544365cd3a5","tid":20619,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:48:38.000Z","msg":"智能穿戴裝置、智能手錶在年前曾經是炙手可熱的產品線，Google 大力發展的 Android Wear 平台最終只算是曇花一現，如今已越見淡靜，各廠產量少之又少。<br />\n<br />\n來到今日，連一度為 Android Wear 領軍開荒的 Motorola，也表明不會在近期推出新的智能手錶，意味著他們將缺席即將上線的 Android Wear 2.0 陣容。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n跟據 Motorola 的全球產品開發主管 Shakil Barkat 的說法，由於 Android Wear 平台的發展並未有甚麼令人興奮的突破，Motorola 方面並未見到市場上對新一代的 Moto 360 產品有太大需求；同時他亦表明，在 Motorola 未來一年的產品路線圖中，並未有推出任何智能裝置的計劃，智能手錶當然也包含在內。<br />\n<br />\n雖然 Shakil Barkat 並未有完全封上 Moto 在智能手錶發展上的後路，然而，Moto 暫別智能手錶市場的事實，對於 Android Wear 陣營以至整個智能手錶業界而言都影響深遠。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;資料來源：AndroidPolice"},{"pid":"e730d4eca6e4a530f46e499870251d7c7c5ed9f3","tid":20619,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T14:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f71119cf2b93ebc500181261973f8dbf19c5675","tid":20619,"uid":623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:00:15.000Z","msg":"鬼有人用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8f5092150f348b0c7fb833e64e34fca74fe5ba","tid":20619,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:48:04.000Z","msg":"watch真心覺得無乜人用"},{"pid":"6867e46627b25db96817bc660e6dcd32d830109c","tid":20619,"uid":40148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:55:18.000Z","msg":"好失望<br />\n<br />\n利申：Moto 360用家"},{"pid":"cf5dea6691d24efa0a5fb6aa9728d3609129c860","tid":20619,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:10:22.000Z","msg":"智能手錶晚晚要叉註定失敗啦"},{"pid":"05ec055e436ac4a4dec6159330a0dd58683558c1","tid":20619,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:25:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>智能手錶晚晚要叉註定失敗啦</blockquote><br />\nmoto360 2015版用家<br />\n喺香港晚晚除錶放床頭叉無乜所謂，但係出trip/旅行真係唔會帶去，又要拎埋個專用叉座，好煩。。。"},{"pid":"cd04b4df4ec9f8a98255027bed2ca5682fcd2093","tid":20619,"uid":14548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:30:18.000Z","msg":"Apple watch都唔hit, android wear點會hit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}